WTEXTMET.OBJ WTEXTOUT.OBJ WVGAMAP.OBJ  WVGAWRT.OBJ  WVISMAP.OBJ  WZORDER.OBJ  \
WVIEWEXT.OBJ WVIEWORG.OBJ WVIEWSCL.OBJ WWINEXT.OBJ  WWINORG.OBJ  WWINSCL.OBJ  \
